Defendant Christopher H Koehn in court with attorney Ronald James Sonderhouse.  Kevin Michael Osborne appeared for the State of Wisconsin.   Defendant enters a plea of no contest to Count 1,  Court finds defendant guilty.  The Defendant was given the following:

WITHHELD SENTENCE;

TERM OF PROBATION:  1 YEAR;

CONDITIONS OF PROBATION:  
*AODA Assessment and follow through with any treatment recommended;
*Perform 50 Hours Community Service.
*Any other condition deemed appropriate by agent.   
*DNA sample to be provided if not yet previously done.

COURT COSTS:  $268.00 (to be paid as a condition of probation);

DNA SURCHARGE:  $250.00 (to be paid as a condition of probation);

Felony warnings, voting rights and firearms warnings given.
